OL,6,FHe said: "I don't even know how to
OL,7,Fmove forward without you. You are my
OL,8,FMum, my best friend, I wish I could
OL,9,Fswap places with you, if I could
OL,10,Fknowing you would be ok I would do it
OL,11,Fin a heartbeat.
OL,13,F"It would be impossible to Thankyou
OL,14,Ffor everything you have done for us,
OL,15,Fyou loved me when I couldn't love
OL,16,Fmyself, you've backed me every step of
OL,17,Fthe way. I really hope I made you just
OL,18,Fthe tiniest bit proud."
OL,20,FIn a statement, Ashton Town FC said
OL,21,Fthe club was "in mourning".
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
