OL,6,FThe club said: "It is with deep
OL,7,Fsadness and a heavy heart that on
OL,8,Fbehalf of Ashton Town FC we announce
OL,9,Fthe tragic death of Debra Wright, wife
OL,10,Fof Chris our Chairman who was
OL,11,Ftragically killed whilst on holiday in
OL,12,FSpain on Saturday evening.
OL,14,F"Our family are in mourning at this
OL,15,Fsad time and we ask for time for Chris
OL,16,Fand his family and everyone at the
OL,17,Fclub to be able to start to come to
OL,18,Fterms with this tragedy."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
