OL,6,FLocal councillor Danny Fletcher posted
OL,7,Fon social media: "Extending my
OL,8,Fheartfelt condolences following the
OL,9,Ftragic passing of Debra, beloved wife
OL,10,Fof Ashton Town FC Chairman, Chris
OL,11,FWright.
OL,13,F"What an amazing family, done so much
OL,14,Ffor our community. My thoughts are
OL,15,Fwith Chris, his family and everyone at
OL,16,FAshton Town FC.
OL,18,F"Anything that Wigan Council can do to
OL,19,Fhelp, they will be there."
