OL,6,FA number of local clubs paid tribute
OL,7,Fto Ms Haines and offered their
OL,8,Fcondolences.
OL,10,FLocal rivals Ashton Athletic wrote:
OL,11,F"We are deeply saddened to hear the
OL,12,Fdevastating news of the passing of
OL,13,FDebra Wright at Ashton Town.
OL,15,F"Everyone at Ashton Athletic sends
OL,16,Ftheir heartfelt condolences to Chris,
OL,17,Fhis family, and all at Ashton Town.
OL,18,FOur thoughts are with you during this
OL,19,Fincredibly difficult time."
