OL,6,FChorley FC added: "Everybody at
OL,7,FChorley sends their heartfelt
OL,8,Fcondolences to all at Ashton Town. Our
OL,9,Fthoughts are with you during this
OL,10,Fincredibly difficult time."
OL,12,FLocal paper Sur in English reported
OL,13,Fthat the Guardia Civil in Malaga said
OL,14,FMs Haines was a passenger on the jet
OL,15,Fski, which was being driven by Mr
OL,16,FWright, when it collided with the
OL,17,Fmotorboat.
